Add 10 War Room visualization enhancements 
 
New visualization component library (src/components/dashboard/visualizations/): 
- DonutRingChart: animated multi-segment ring replacing flat fee distribution bar 
- Sparkline: pure SVG inline micro-charts for trend visualization 
- RollingDigits: airport departure board style number animations 
- ArcGauge: 180 degree instrument panel gauge with spring-physics needle 
- RadialVoteWheel: concentric arc vote visualization for governance 
- CandlestickStrip: inline 24H mini candlestick price chart 
- FlameTimeline: vertical timeline with fire-themed nodes for distributions 
- TierPyramid: stacking multiplier tier pyramid with active tier glow 
- DataFlowParticles: canvas particle stream along tab bar 
 
Integrations: 
- ReflectionsIntel: ArcGauge replaces linear meter, DonutRingChart replaces stacked bar, FlameTimeline replaces table 
- CommandHeader: inline CandlestickStrip next to USD price 
- GovernanceTab: RadialVoteWheel on proposals with votes 
- BurnOperations: FlameTimeline replaces transaction table 
- MultiplierTiers: TierPyramid replaces flat grid 
- WarRoomTabBar: DataFlowParticles stream across top 
 
Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com> 
